# Backend — FastAPI

## Точка входа

```python
# backend/app/main.py
@asynccontextmanager
async def lifespan(app: FastAPI):
    await run_migrations()          # Alembic при старте
    await settings_service.load_cache()  # system_settings + data_providers
    scheduler.start()               # ETL cron, digest, renewal
    yield
    scheduler.shutdown()

app = FastAPI(lifespan=lifespan)
```

